Introduction

Koko is a Japanese dancer, rapper, and singer under WAKEONE.

In 2024, she was a contestant on Mnet's survival show I-LAND2: N/a, where she ended up ranking 4th place in the final with 320,124 votes, thus securing her spot as a member of the final group, izna.

Koko made her debut with the group on November 25, 2024, with the release of their first mini album titled "N/a".
